reviewText: Best Movie, EVER! Good wholesome fun for everyone!

Definitely we need to see more of him. This man is not just the best actor to ever hit the silver screen, from what I know of him, he is a genius! Where is he? Bring back R. Terrell Reagan! Your fans for are calling for you.
Funny - Creative - We need more movies like this! - Where is R. Terrell Reagan today - he needs to make more movies!
